data.description: Welcome to this stunning and meticulously renovated home on an oversized lot! This property boasts upgrades and improvements that are sure to impress. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by the perfect blend of style, functionality, and durability. The heart of this home is the kitchen, featuring exquisite leather granite counts, all new appliances, brand-new backsplash, fixtures and more! Rest easy knowing that the foundation of this home has a lifetime warranty, ensuring your peace of mind for years to come. Other updates include new plumbing, ceiling fans, base boards, doors, fencing, outdoor paint and electrical. The AC is 4 years old and the roof 5 years old. The property has been professionally staged, allowing you to envision yourself living in this beautifully updated home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own, combining modern convenience with timeless style. It's the perfect place to create lasting memories and call home.
